metadata.name: My Tasty Choco Donut
metadata.description:
Hello everyone! This is ''My Tasty Choco Donut." Right now, it's mine, but if you'd like, you can make it yours. I have also created this Donut NFT in real life! I tried my best to make it as similar as I could, and it was crazy delicious! If you would like, you can take a look at my real-life donut as well! You can find multiple videos about how I have created my Donut NFT in real life on my Twitter, Instagram, TikTok, and YouTube! So, check it out if you'd like!

My Tasty Choco Donut is a very tasty chocolate donut with pretty colored sprinkles. The colors of the sprinkles that I have chosen are white, baby blue, bright blue, lilac, purple, and pink. The icing is, of course, as you can see a chocolate icing. 

You should try recreating My Tasty Choco Donut in real life as well; maybe you can do better. Who knows? 

My Tasty Choco Donut is twirling in the bright blue sky, and the sprinkles are dancing happily behind it. What a mouth-watering sight...
